ZH: 我每天早上起床第一件事就是刷牙。
EN: The first thing I do every morning when I wake up is brush my teeth.

ZH: 我用电动牙刷刷牙，效果特别好。
EN: I use an electric toothbrush to brush my teeth, it works really well.

ZH: 刷牙的时间应该持续至少两分钟。
EN: Brushing your teeth should last at least two minutes.

ZH: 我刷牙时总是习惯先用牙线清洁牙缝。
EN: I always make it a habit to floss before brushing my teeth.

ZH: 刷牙后记得漱口以保持口气清新。
EN: Remember to rinse your mouth after brushing to keep your breath fresh.

ZH: 我的牙刷是特别为敏感牙龈设计的。
EN: My toothbrush is specially designed for sensitive gums.

ZH: 我刷牙时经常听音乐来增加乐趣。
EN: I often listen to music while brushing my teeth to make it more enjoyable.

ZH: 我用草莓口味的牙膏刷牙，味道很好。
EN: I brush my teeth with strawberry-flavored toothpaste, it tastes great.

ZH: 手术后刷牙要特别轻柔以避免伤害口腔。
EN: After surgery, brushing your teeth should be done very gently to avoid injuring your mouth.

ZH: 孩子们每天晚上刷牙前都会一起唱歌。
EN: The kids sing together every night before brushing their teeth.

ZH: 刷牙应该是每个人日常生活中至关重要的部分。
EN: Brushing teeth should be an essential part of everyone's daily routine.

ZH: 刷牙前不妨尝一尝牙膏的味道。
EN: Before brushing your teeth, you can try the taste of the toothpaste.

ZH: 刷牙时要注意牙刷的角度和力度。
EN: When brushing your teeth, pay attention to the angle and pressure of the toothbrush.

ZH: 在户外旅行时，要记得随身携带牙刷和牙膏。
EN: When traveling outdoors, remember to bring your toothbrush and toothpaste with you.

ZH: 在公共场所刷牙要注意不影响他人。
EN: When brushing your teeth in public places, be mindful not to disturb others.

ZH: 刷牙后还要拔草擦牙龈来保持口腔清洁。
EN: After brushing your teeth, you should also use a tongue scraper to keep your mouth clean.

ZH: 刷牙应该是日常生活中的必修课。
EN: Brushing teeth should be a required course in daily life.

ZH: 坚持每天刷牙可以减少牙齿问题的发生。
EN: Consistently brushing teeth every day can reduce the occurrence of dental problems.

ZH: 刷牙是一项简单但重要的卫生习惯。
EN: Brushing teeth is a simple yet important hygiene habit.
